original_title: Bosse Högberg - en film om kärlek, sjukdom och feta smällar
overview: Bosse Högberg - once a tough European champion in light-middleweight since suffering from aphasia after stroke in 1988. The toughest fighter of Sweden ever. Against a Frenchman, he boxed fifteen rounds with the rejected jawbone.
title: Bosse Högberg - en film om kärlek, sjukdom och feta smällar
